to connect to the dashboard:
1)Use SSH port forwarding
SSH into your Vagrant VM with port forwarding:
    vagrant ssh -- -L 8001:127.0.0.1:8001
This maps port 8001 on your host to port 8001 on the VM.

2)Inside the VM, run:
    sudo k3s kubectl proxy --address='0.0.0.0' --accept-hosts='^.*$'

--address='0.0.0.0' allows connections from outside the VM.

--accept-hosts='^.*$' allows any host to connect (safe locally).

3)On your host machine, open browser:
    http://localhost:8001/api/v1/namespaces/kubernetes-dashboard/services/https:kubernetes-dashboard:/proxy/